edulution-linbo-plugin (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Edulution LINBO Plugin
  * REST API with JWT auth, WebSocket, host management
  * React frontend with dark theme
  * Delta-Sync from linuxmuster-api (port 8001)
  * DHCP scaffold with PXE boot options
  * Image sync (HTTP range + torrent)
  * SSH terminal (xterm.js)
  * Driver management (patchclass)
  * systemd hardening (ProtectSystem, MemoryMax)
  * Production audit: 22 security + reliability fixes

 -- Edulution <info@edulution.io>  Mon, 24 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0100
